                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "ATTACHMENT A"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                416,
                92,
                581,
                111
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "I. The Subject Devices to Be Searched"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 2
            },
            "bbox": [
                124,
                123,
                449,
                141
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "The Subject Devices are particularly described as compact discs stored in containers marked with FBI evidence numbers 15, 16, 17, 18, and 22, seized from the residence located at 9 East 71st Street, New York, New York, on or about July 7, 2019."
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                122,
                154,
                872,
                206
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "II. Items to Be Seized"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 2
            },
            "bbox": [
                124,
                219,
                315,
                238
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "A. Evidence, Fruits, and Instrumentalities of the Subject Offenses"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 2
            },
            "bbox": [
                150,
                251,
                700,
                270
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "This warant authorizes the seizure of certain evidence, fruits, and instrumentalities of violations of Title 18, United States Code, Sections 1591 (sex trafficking of minors), and 371 (sex trafficking conspiracy) (the \"Subject Offenses\") described as follows:"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                122,
                285,
                872,
                338
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "1. Any documents or communications with or regarding victims or potential victims of the Subject Offenses;"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                122,
                349,
                870,
                383
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "2. Any photographs of victims or potential victims of the Subject Offnses;"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                178,
                396,
                797,
                414
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "3. Any nude, partially nude, or sexually suggestive photographs of individuals who appear to be teenage girls, or younger;"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                122,
                427,
                870,
                462
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "4. Motion pictures, films, videos, and other recordings of visual or written depictions of minors engaged in sexually explicit conduct, as defined in 18 U.S.C. s 2256(2);"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                120,
                474,
                870,
                511
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "5. Records or other items that evidence ownership, control, or use of, or access to devices, storage media, and related electronic equipment used to access, transmit, or store information relating to the Subject Offenses, including, but not limited to, sales receipts, warranties, bills for Internet access, handwritten notes, registry entries, configuration files, saved usernames and passwords, user profiles, e-mail contacts, and photographs;"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                120,
                522,
                872,
                608
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "6. Any child erotica, defined as suggestive visual depictions of nude minors that do not constitute child pornography as defined by 18 U.S.C. $ 2256(8)."
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                120,
                618,
                870,
                655
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "B. Review of ESI"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 2
            },
            "bbox": [
                150,
                666,
                307,
                683
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "Law enforcement personnel (including, in addition to law enforcement officers and agents, and depending on the nature of the ESI and the status of the investigation and related proceedings, attorneys for the government, attorney support staff, agency personnel assisting the government in this investigation, and outside technical experts under government control) will create a forensic image of the Subject Devices (if practicable) and review the ESI contained therein for information responsive to the warrant."
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                120,
                697,
                870,
                800
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "In conducting this review, law enforcement personnel may use various techniques to determine which files or other ESI contain evidence or fruits of the Subject Offenses. Such techniques may include, for example:"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                120,
                813,
                870,
                866
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "page_footer",
            "content": {
                "page_footer_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "2017.08.02"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                122,
                882,
                194,
                897
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "page_footer",
            "content": {
                "page_footer_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "SDNY_GM_00000136"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                741,
                901,
                874,
                916
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "page_footer",
            "content": {
                "page_footer_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "EFTA_00114220"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                861,
                946,
                978,
                962
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "page_footer",
